task.summary: Removed example code from Spring controller. Tentatively implemented request caching (on the side of the simulcast fetcher library).

Fixed bug that was causing items that shifted days to not be sorted by time properly.
(Of course the timestamps aren't going to be ordered properly if the days differ.. gg me)
Calendar picker now filters out calendars that the user only has 'reader' permissions for. https://trello.com/c/6LwMMhI1
User can now choose to create a new calendar to create items in.
Added 'open Calendar' dialog after events have been created.
